      <div class="msgContentFrame">So, as I`m getting past lvl 10 as Goldsmith and Miner, I`m starting to wonder wich types of equipment should I use to craft and how to get then. <br />So far, I`ve been using the basic lvl 1 equipment that I got when I started as THM, plus choker and rings that I did myself. But when I try to get HQ or some other recipies, I utterly fail. I saw somebody talking about +crafting equipment on some other thread, but I cant really find it. <br />Can you guys point me out how and when you guys got those? <br />Thanks in advance.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>FFXIV, dead till &quot;December&quot;: <br /><a href="http://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=5577442" title="http://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=5577442" rel="external nofollow">http://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=5577442</a> <br /> <br />WoW, reborn: <br /><a href="http://www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Aerie+Peak&amp;n=Lothildin" title="http://www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Aerie+Peak&amp;n=Lothildin" rel="external nofollow">http://www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Aerie+Peak&amp;n=Lothildin</a></div></div>
