      <div class="msgContentFrame">If you check out the database of gear you can search by stats and slots.  The stats that help crafting are control, Magical Craftsmanship and craftsmanship iirc.  For gathering you're looking for output and perception (and another I can't remember?).  Mostly I've found these on cloth and leather; less on metal armor.  The biggest improvement I've gotten in crafting performance always comes when I upgrade my tools (good luck finding the 20+ ones though -_-). <br /> <br />Edit: duh, the other gathering stat is &quot;gathering&quot; <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Oct 19th 2010  8:44am by sharneee </span></i></div>
